                <li class="tech-spec p-4 glassmorphism" id="spec1">
                  <h3 class="orbitron text-xl font-bold mb-2" data-text="spec1Title">AI Neural Network</h3>
                  <p data-text="spec1Desc">Advanced 12-core quantum neural processor with 1.2 trillion parameters for real-time decision making and obstacle avoidance.</p>
